<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12257</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23063</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“再见，魔法师。”骑士说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23064</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32516</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他出去后，汤姆“砰”的关上门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32517</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37375</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他一点都不想帮那个坏骑士。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37376</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41790</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>猫咪在舔自己的爪子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41791</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46713</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我该怎么办，猫咪？”汤姆问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46714</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53025</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我去和马谈谈。”她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53026</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60920</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那天晚上，汤姆去了赛场。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60921</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67770</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>骑士骑在马上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67771</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72704</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！”骑士大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72705</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79701</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>马把他从背上扔下来了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86781</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这马太差了！”骑士说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86782</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91594</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看上去很生气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91595</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95788</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它从来不听我的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95789</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98159</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要施咒语了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98160</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101196</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你准备好了吗？”汤姆问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101197</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103878</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哈哈！”骑士大笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103879</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106200</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我当然准备好了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106201</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107676</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你这个傻瓜。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107677</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110864</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我要得到所有的奖金！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110865</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118055</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆挥动了他的魔杖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118056</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123914</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>噗！赛场上出现了浓烟。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123915</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132909</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>猫咪溜过去跟马说话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132910</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137792</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>几分钟后，浓烟散去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137793</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141899</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我已经施过咒语了。”汤姆说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141900</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147707</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很好。”坏骑士说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147708</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153658</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他回到了马背上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153659</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161710</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>骑士骑着马在赛场走来走去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161711</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这一次，他的马没有再把他扔下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170236</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175188</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这一次，马听他的话了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175189</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你的咒语很有用，魔法师！”骑士说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180986</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184301</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他露出了贪婪的笑容。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184302</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206590</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“奖金全都是我的了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>